title: FOIA Request for SEC Briefs – Administrative Proceeding File No. 3-14081

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Please provide any documents responsive to request #13-09881-FOIA, received on Aug. 1, 2013 and completed on August 16, 2013

The subject of the initial request is copied below:

SEC briefs for Administrative Proceeding File No. 3-14081

I am seeking any updates or reports related to this proceeding. If these updates or reports are connected  with additional documents, please include those also.

I request a waiver of all fees associated with this request as this information will be used for educational purposes only and is not for commercial use.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Benjamin Cooper

title: FOIA request for Title IX investigations completed by Michigan State University

communications.communication:
To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Michigan Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Please provide any documents responsive to request #17-01810-F, received on May 26, 2017.

Specifically I am requesting: 

1. All records concerning Title IX investigations completed by Michigan State University between May 1, 2017 and May 24, 2017. 

2.  Any final reports or outcomes related to this investigation, if applicable. 

Include all documents pertaining to these records including investigation summaries.

If there are any fees associated with this request, please notify me in advance. I am requesting a fee waiver because this request is for research purposes.

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 5 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Benjamin Cooper
